{"tid":1347524,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[幫手share] 元朗事件傷左既可以去claim返港鐵第三者保險","createTime":"2019-07-22T06:15:59.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-22T11:47:34.000Z","uid":159103,"like":75,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":29,"replies":[{"pid":"5033736f947918cfa822ee9c0ba5342f70ebfd82","tid":1347524,"uid":159103,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T06:15:59.000Z","msg":"元朗站白衣黨無差別襲擊途人事件︰<br />\n本人今日曾致電港鐵公司，代表港鐵公司既 馮偉程先生( 當天當值經理) 表示, 就元朗站白衣黨無差別襲擊途人示件，可以正式向地鐵公司遞交書面通知，申請第三者保險賠償港鐵，港鐵公司聲稱收到遞交後, 會有專員處理 (並不代表一定會賠償)<br />\n如有疑問，請致電港鐵熱線︰2881 8888 馮偉程先生 內線電話: 1206 ，如遇馮偉程先生休假或病假，請致電另一當值服務經理 陳先生, 內線電話︰1208<br />\n<br />\n以書面或Fax或網站上的意見提交方式遞交，內容包括︰<br />\n<br />\n1. 當時狀況<br />\n2. 要求賠償<br />\n3. 聯絡方法<br />\n<br />\n郵寄地址︰九龍灣偉業街33號德福廣場港鐵總部大樓 港鐵公司 公司事務處收<br />\n<br />\n網上提交: <a href=\"http://www.mtr.com.hk/ch/customer/main/contact_us.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.mtr.com.hk%2Fch%2Fcustomer%2Fmain%2Fcontact_us.html&d=wUVL7ECAGG5qyTf5%2FTxhHwsTF5hDypdTwPi8eTnvKzQ%3D&h=7596054b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.mtr.com.hk/ch/customer/main/contact_us.html</a><br />\n(謹記，一定要選擇 請回覆 電話 / 電郵)<br />\n<br />\nFax: 2208 3161"},{"pid":"b0ad3c851d995a049bffec043555836cbc39bd4f","tid":1347524,"uid":159103,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T06:16:09.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"d9bba2f4063f88f336716eae524c8a37b3da05f4","tid":1347524,"uid":159103,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T06:16:31.000Z","msg":"大家幫手話比其他人知"},{"pid":"164225490ff1468fc6da4c8245370346ac102883","tid":1347524,"uid":159103,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T06:16:47.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e7fd431659a43cd2b2b8ce6b0b04bcdb7560a071","tid":1347524,"uid":159103,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T06:18:37.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"fd9d656b99ae3fe94779c5306e3dadb178ab08cd","tid":1347524,"uid":23815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"